title: Sound On: Cuba Protests, Voting Rights
itunes:title: Sound On: Cuba Protests, Voting Rights
description:
Guest hosts Jack Fitzpatrick and Emily Wilkins spoke to Bloomberg White house reporter Justin Sink, Aaron Brown, former managing director and head of financial market research at AQR Capital Management, Colorado Secretary of State Jena Griswold and Bloomberg Politics contributors Rick Davis and Jeanne Sheehan Zaino.
